msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:68
msgid ""
"As can be seen in the images above, faces that touch each other will deform "
"when rotated when the pivot point is set to Individual Origins. Faces that "
"do not touch will rotate around their Individual Origins (their center)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:78
msgid "Scaling with non-touching faces."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/transform/transform_control/pivot_point/individual_origins.rst:83
